Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.69,0:01:33.88,Default,YSis,0000,0000,0000,,Maccachin stole some buns, \Nand they got stuck in his throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.35,0:01:35.15,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:36.90,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Go back to Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:40.72,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Can you be Yuri's coach tomorrow, \Nfor just one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.06,0:01:41.72,Default,Others,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:42.33,Default,Others,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:42.72,Default,Others,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:45.70,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, this is a crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.24,0:01:48.46,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Ask Yakov anything you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:52.22,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,If you're in trouble, just hug him,\Nand he'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.77,0:01:54.38,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Yuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.38,0:01:57.22,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm not here, I'll always \Nbe with you in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:01.96,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,And then Victor went back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.49,0:02:07.50,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Ninth Skate \N{\fs20}Yuri vs. Yuri \NThe Horror!! Rostelecom Cup, Free Skate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:07.50,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri vs. Yuri. The Horror!! \NRostelecom Cup, Free Skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:10.54,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it didn't look like you exchanged \Nany words with Coach Yakov
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:12.50,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,at this morning's public practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.07,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just do what I've always done \Nin practice with Victor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:20.36,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Yakov take on that pork cutlet bowl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:23.89,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, your grandfather's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.12,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa, I thought you weren't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:29.87,Default,YGramps,0000,0000,0000,,Just try these.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:33.67,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,There's pork cutlet, scrambled \Neggs, and white rice in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.67,0:02:34.65,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this pirozhki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.65,0:02:36.40,Default,YGramps,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pork cutlet bowl pirozhki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:39.38,Default,YGramps,0000,0000,0000,,Eat them and do well in today's \Nfree skate, Yuratchka.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:41.98,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.66,0:02:45.89,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,With Victor gone, I'm the only one who can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.66,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Everything should be on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.66,0:02:50.14,arena,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Moscow Small Sports Arena \NMoscow, Russia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:51.23,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The Rostelecom Cup, the last \Nevent in the Grand Prix Series.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:54.92,order,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sixth Event, Rostelecom Cup\NMen's Short Program Skating Order\N{\fs16}Emil Nekola\NMichele Crispino\NSeung Gil Lee\NYuri Plisetsky\NKatsuki Yuri\NJean-Jacques Leroy
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.35,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Group Two is finally about to start \Nin the Men's Singles Free Skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.33,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Each skater comes into this event \Nwith his own hopes and fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.33,0:03:00.65,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,This event will determine who advances \Nto the Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.18,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Group Two's first competitor,\Ncurrently in sixth place,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:05.68,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,is the Czech Republic's Emil Nekola, age 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.27,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He is skating to music from \Nthe movie {\i1}Anastasis{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:13.29,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His theme is "Cyberpunk: \NI've ceased to be human."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:18.17,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Just as his theme suggests, he's planned \Nfour quads, a superhuman feat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.20,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple Salchow. Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:21.58,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.54,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is a quadruple jump combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:33.33,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,Quadruple toe loop, triple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.33,0:03:35.06,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this opportunity \Nto clarify something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:39.34,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make it to the Grand Prix Final\Nwith or without your help, Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:43.82,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,So you need to win without \Nmy support, too, Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:52.22,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His next jump will also be a quad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.51,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.51,0:03:54.61,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:03.18,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not every woman in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:04.85,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,You need to get out more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:07.30,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need any other woman but you, Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:11.58,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to focus on skating and come \Nthis far because you were with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:14.33,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me alone, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.33,0:04:16.77,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Become strong, Michele Crispino!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.60,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I can skate without your love,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.60,0:04:19.69,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll start dating!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:24.05,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,If he finishes in second or above, \Nhe may still make the Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:28.53,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like Czech men \Nwho have nothing but cheer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:32.56,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Or do you like moody Japanese men \Nwho look like closet pervs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.45,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your short program was super sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.56,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:36.76,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,So despite being Italian, you don't \Nlike men who are negative, Sala?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:37.84,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:39.32,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,That was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:42.70,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,So far, we've seen four flawless quads!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.46,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,He's not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.46,0:04:46.09,Default - italics,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.91,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,He'd planned a combination there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:54.77,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He fell and couldn't complete the second jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.85,Default - italics,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.04,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple Salchow—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.52,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.98,Default - italics,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,Still going strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:15.36,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The score for the Czech Republic's \NEmil Nekola is 189.15.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:18.54,Ranking,,0000,0000,0000,,RK: 1\NEmil Nekola     Total
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:18.54,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His total score is 271.58. \NHe's currently in first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:16.82,Default,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.54,Default,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.57,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,Sala, you're not rinkside to \Nsend him off to the ice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.87,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,We now have Italy's Michele Crispino, age 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.07,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He finished the short program in fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:29.55,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Will he make a comeback in the free skate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.16,0:05:33.46,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He is skating to "Serenade for Two."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.64,0:05:39.34,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Sala, are you watching me \Nsomewhere out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:43.13,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell, even when we're apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.34,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple Salchow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:52.53,Default - italics,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Mickey might be feeling a little down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:08.98,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple flip, single loop, and a triple Salchow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:10.34,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A three-jump combo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:15.49,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do with my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:20.60,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple axel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:25.49,Default - italics,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to practice, his skating \Nis much more mellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.17,0:06:28.31,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a completely different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:29.50,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.68,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.68,0:06:35.43,Default,Popo,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel lost love in Michele's skating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:41.24,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Sala, we've been inseparable since birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.98,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,My precious Sala...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.69,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,My lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:49.03,Default - flashback,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Why are boys mean to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:51.28,Default - flashback,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:53.51,Default - flashback,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:55.76,Default - flashback,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I got asked on a date again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:57.79,Default - flashback,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.04,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.10,0:07:03.50,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:13.68,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Sala, this is the last time that I skate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:18.61,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,My love ends here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:23.94,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,This is my real love.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:27.56,Default - italics,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, Sala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.60,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:47.17,Default,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Flawless!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:01.62,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Here come the scores for \NMichele Crispino of Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.60,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His score is 193.24!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:08.71,Ranking,,0000,0000,0000,,RK: 1\NMichele Crispino     Total
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.31,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His total score is 282.89.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:09.43,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's surpassed his personal best \Nby almost twenty points!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:10.57,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Mickey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:12.95,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.79,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.45,0:08:19.71,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,That was the coolest program \NI've seen from you so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:21.85,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,You thought of me when you \Nwere skating, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.85,0:08:23.08,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.08,0:08:26.06,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for saying such mean things earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:27.73,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:30.09,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,We're better apart, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.94,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:32.71,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Seung Gil's starting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:33.47,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.71,0:08:42.76,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yakov.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.76,0:08:43.74,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.74,0:08:45.52,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'm changing the jump composition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:49.19,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll reduce the number of jumps in \Nthe first half from four to two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.19,0:08:51.16,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,So you'll have six in the second half?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:51.99,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:53.17,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.95,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I can't win against JJ or Yuri otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:07.71,Ranking,,0000,0000,0000,,RK: 3\NSeung Gil Lee     Total
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.93,0:09:07.71,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Although Seung Gil Lee recovered after \Na fall on his early quadruple loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he suffered a huge loss in the standings
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:11.79,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,and lost hope of advancing \Nto the Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.64,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,But we look forward to seeing him in \Nthe Four Continents Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:19.89,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Here on his home turf,\Nwe have Yuri Plisetsky, age 15,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.89,0:09:27.07,Default,Audience,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yuri! Yuri! Yuri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:21.95,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,in third place after the short program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:23.89,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to those cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.89,0:09:28.27,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win the first gold of my senior debut here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:34.74,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He is skating to \N"Allegro Appassionato in B Minor."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.74,0:09:37.28,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The program was choreographed \Nby Lilia Baranovskaya,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.11,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,former principal of the Bolshoi Ballet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.33,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,For Yuri Plisetsky's senior debut,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:45.47,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,they've chosen a piece well-known for its \Ndifficulty and heart-pounding intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.07,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's been allowed to attempt \Nquads since his senior debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.67,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the first of two in this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:53.82,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,As in his short program, \Nhe landed that with confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:00.14,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple axel from a spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:04.31,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,That was really high. \NDoesn't he seem too psyched up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.31,0:10:05.33,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:06.77,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Dance with beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.55,0:10:10.37,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Beauty is a crushing force of righteousness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.37,0:10:14.15,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Strength means nothing without beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:27.40,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A hellish step sequence \Nwithout even time for a breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:29.17,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How is he so calm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:32.39,Default - italics,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,This is right around when he starts to tire.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.39,0:10:34.20,Default - italics,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Hold out in the second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.55,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn, this is tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.63,0:10:40.80,Default - italics,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,He's putting six jumps in the second half?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.65,0:10:44.03,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go with the second-half jumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.68,0:10:45.63,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:53.07,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Pork cutlet bowl has three quads,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.07,0:10:54.82,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,and JJ has four.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:56.44,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:05.39,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,To beat them, I can't make any mistakes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.69,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:10.22,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a choreographic sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.47,0:11:13.38,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to lose like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:19.17,Default - flashback,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,With all eyes on him during the free skate, \NYuri Plisetsky of Russia, age 15,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:20.76,Default - flashback,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,is now in first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:21.36,Default - flashback,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:28.87,Default - flashback,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Let's climb the podium together again \Nat the Rostelecom Cup, Yuri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.62,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That shithead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.80,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,Quadruple Salchow, triple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.90,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful jump with great height!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:39.41,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's showing tremendous spirit \Nin his program's second half.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.37,0:11:49.18,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple loop, double toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:54.60,Default - italics,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the last jump combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:56.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really Yurio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.58,0:12:01.01,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple axel, single loop, and a triple Salchow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:02.86,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He landed all his jumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.47,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,At the Rostelecom Cup of the Grand \NPrix Series, his senior debut,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:13.10,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,he's brushed off the pressure and \Nresponded to his local fans,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.21,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,delivering a sublime free skate program!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.06,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,A performance beyond his limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:32.08,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That must've been what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:34.09,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Plisetsky from Russia.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:39.59,Ranking,,0000,0000,0000,,RK: 1\NYuri Plisetsky     Total
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.09,0:12:38.59,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His free skate score is 199.87, a personal best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.59,0:12:41.80,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His total score is 297.96.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:43.24,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's currently in first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:45.23,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's won a ticket to the Grand Prix Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:47.57,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like my free skate, pork cutlet bowl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.65,0:12:59.77,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki Yuri from Japan is in second \Nplace after the short program.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.42,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He is skating to "Yuri on Ice."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:09.17,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want them to think \Neverything Victor's taught me
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:10.95,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,has been a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.09,0:13:13.98,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have to prove that by winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.86,0:13:17.31,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If I fail here, everything is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.67,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.21,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I popped it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:22.19,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,What's that pork cutlet bowl doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:24.46,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His second jump turned into a single.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:25.59,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:27.60,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:33.63,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How do I recover from this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:39.08,Default - flashback,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you tend to flub your jumps \Nwhen something is on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:41.61,Default - flashback,V,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'm your coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:45.11,Default - flashback,V,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you win the Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.01,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,How did he know how I felt?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.74,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Until Victor came into my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:53.71,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I could never openly say that I'd win gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:57.64,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,but I never skated with the thought \Nin my mind that I'd lose anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.04,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,That jump had enough rotations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.04,0:14:03.90,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Truthfully, I wanted to win gold at \Nlast year's Grand Prix Final, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:06.44,Default - flashback,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, you're not weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.68,Default - flashback,V,0000,0000,0000,,No one else thinks that, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:12.28,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I know what love \Nis and am stronger for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.28,0:14:15.45,Default - flashback,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prove it to myself with a \NGrand Prix Final gold medal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:19.65,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to come this far \Nbecause Victor believed in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:20.49,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:22.40,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,If I end here without making \Nthe Grand Prix Final...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.61,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,He two-footed that landing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:25.34,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.89,0:14:26.86,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.18,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:29.03,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.93,Default,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:35.23,Default,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,All supportive now that you've \Nclinched your spot in the Final, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.23,0:14:36.87,Default,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer for me, too, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.35,Default,Lilia,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.03,0:14:43.54,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yurio looked like he'd kick the bucket \Non his last three-jump combo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:47.77,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I have more stamina than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.92,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple axel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.56,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Whether Victor were with me or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.50,0:14:58.15,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,it would still feel just as tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.60,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple flip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.95,0:15:02.59,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:07.84,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one who can skate this \Nprogram with this much appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.20,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple axel, single loop, and triple Salchow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.72,0:15:22.71,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple Lutz, triple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.96,0:15:26.63,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who loves this \Nprogram Victor and I made
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:29.26,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,the most in the whole world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.01,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not finished yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:36.49,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be done when I get the gold with Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:41.01,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,You can feel Katsuki Yuri's love, \Na love he can only express on the ice,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.01,0:15:43.69,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,in this step sequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.21,0:15:57.35,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, he had really good flow until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.64,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:00.86,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,When you think of how it could've \Nbeen with Victor here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.86,0:16:02.10,Default,Mila,0000,0000,0000,,you really want to see that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:22.48,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,That was the toughest program \NI've done so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:25.97,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.48,0:16:30.46,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,You totally failed to take advantage \Nof the program Vitya made for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:34.49,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you practice for the \Npossibility that you might flub a jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:37.98,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,He's just like Victor... A huge \Nlecture at the kiss and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:37.04,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Victor never did, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:39.53,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I guess he never learned differently as a coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.98,0:16:39.82,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,We have Katsuki Yuri's scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.99,0:16:45.00,Ranking,,0000,0000,0000,,RK: 3\NKatsuki Yuri     Total
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.82,0:16:41.77,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His free skate score is 172.87.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:44.08,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His total score is 282.84.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.08,0:16:45.90,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's currently in third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:48.38,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He may yet advance to the Grand Prix Final,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.38,0:16:49.73,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,but we won't know until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.48,0:16:52.16,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,That's a higher score than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:55.22,Default,Yakov,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:56.76,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Spasibo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.27,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Victor will go back to Russia soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:05.27,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,The final competitor is \NJean-Jacques Leroy, age 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.64,0:17:07.27,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.00,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you all agree, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.91,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He is skating to "Partizan Hope."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:21.20,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Katsuki, Victor may have chosen you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.41,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,but you're no king.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.39,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell that much by your free skate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.03,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,I am the only king!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:28.00,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple Salchow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.00,0:17:28.81,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.26,0:17:31.69,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's planned four quads in this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:34.38,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,If all of them are successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.38,0:17:35.60,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,his free skate program
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.60,0:17:39.24,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,has the highest technical difficulty \Namong all the skaters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.24,0:17:42.70,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is a quad-triple combination.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.97,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,Quadruple toe loop, triple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.15,0:17:49.03,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,At Skate Canada, this year's\Nfirst Grand Prix event,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.03,0:17:51.66,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,he held off Russia's Yuri Plisetsky, \Nwinning for the second time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:54.23,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,In last year's Grand Prix Final, \Nhe finished third.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.23,0:17:56.47,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,With Victor Nikiforov absent this season,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.54,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,a new prince in the figure skating \Nworld has been born.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.44,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:04.03,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:05.59,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,I'm already a king!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.08,0:18:11.19,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll be the hero who stops \NVictor from becoming the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:12.92,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,consecutive five-time world champion."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.59,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I was thinking \Nwhen I made this program,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:17.67,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,but I had no idea Victor would go on break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.04,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he ran because he was \Nafraid of losing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:24.14,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,That poor guy, Victor Nikiforov!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.80,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple axel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.60,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.69,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,my precious girlfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.05,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,the great people of Canada,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:38.57,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone who loves skating...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.55,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.32,0:18:44.13,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't enough love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.13,0:18:45.01,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple Lutz.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.01,0:18:46.60,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Nailed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.57,0:18:51.21,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just that I land all the jumps with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:55.24,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,They're integrated into the overall \Nperformance, are they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:59.44,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A triple flip, single loop, and triple Salchow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.44,0:19:00.30,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:01.78,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,A superb jump combination!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:02.81,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, judges!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.81,0:19:04.82,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,This is JJ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.93,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,His last jump will be a quad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.93,0:19:09.35,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,So far, there have been no mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.95,Default - italics,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:12.33,Default,Oda,0000,0000,0000,,A quadruple toe loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:14.44,Default,Moro,0000,0000,0000,,He's landed all his jumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.37,Default,News,0000,0000,0000,,JJ will take first in the free skate, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:19.90,Default,News,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri Plisetsky will place second,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:21.65,Default,News,0000,0000,0000,,with Michele Crispino in third.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.65,0:19:23.22,Default,News,0000,0000,0000,,Katsuki Yuri will be fourth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:25.10,Default,News,0000,0000,0000,,When you total both competition scores,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:27.84,Default,News,0000,0000,0000,,Michele and Katsuki have \Nthe same overall score.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:29.41,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're tied in points,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.41,0:19:33.46,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I can squeak into the Final because \NI placed second in the Cup of China.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:42.57,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Rostelecom Cup is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.85,0:19:46.84,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The final six who will advance \Nto the Grand Prix Final are
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.84,0:19:49.33,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,the three who had basically \Nbeen confirmed already...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.58,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,JJ, who cemented his win \Nwith another high score,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.09,0:19:54.60,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yurio, who finished second, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:57.18,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:20:01.05,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to come support me at the \NWomen's Free Skate tomorrow, Mickey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:03.02,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Can't I at least cheer you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.02,0:20:05.18,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,You'd just rush right to the kiss and cry again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:09.04,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri, congrats on qualifying \Nfor the Grand Prix Final!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.82,Default,Sala,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.82,0:20:12.07,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Sala!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:12.88,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.52,0:20:15.52,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:16.73,Default,Miche,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.28,Default,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,Was that Mickey screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.39,Default,Emil,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? A hugging competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.40,Default,JJ,0000,0000,0000,,JJ is—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.66,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:30.66,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:40.22,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'm this close to the peak of my \Ncompetitive figure skating career.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.65,0:20:42.51,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I really want the gold now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:45.68,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,The Grand Prix Final will be my last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.73,0:20:48.95,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't win gold,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:53.61,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have Victor step down as coach \Nafter the Grand Prix Final, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.24,0:20:58.35,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, pork cutlet bowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.35,0:20:59.65,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You made me look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.96,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yurio...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.64,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,What was that earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:04.13,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Stop creeping me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.13,0:21:05.72,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,And what was that free skate, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:09.45,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You can make the excuse that you couldn't do your best because Victor wasn't there,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:13.79,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,but I was in top form and \Nearned a new personal best,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:15.46,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,only to lose to JJ again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:18.95,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You have no right to feel more \Ndown than me, pork cutlet bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:23.65,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.22,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost your birthday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.08,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:30.97,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Pirozhki?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.97,0:21:31.89,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.89,0:21:33.13,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:33.98,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:38.77,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,There's rice in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.77,0:21:40.66,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Pork cutlet and egg, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:41.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pork cutlet bowl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.81,0:21:42.47,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.72,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,My grandpa made them himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.49,Default,Yuri,0000,0000,0000,,Great, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.49,0:21:46.51,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.80,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,They're vkusno!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:52.48,airport,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukuoka Airport International Terminal
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:52.48,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot I want to tell you, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.09,0:21:55.19,Default - italics,Y,0000,0000,0000,,What do I say first?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:20.31,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.31,0:22:24.36,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about what I can \Ndo as your coach from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.42,0:22:26.81,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.06,0:22:38.40,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my coach until I retire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:47.80,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like a marriage proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.58,0:22:58.55,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you'd never retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:06.28,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Let's win gold together at \Nthe Grand Prix Final.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:09.99,TBC,,0000,0000,0000,,To Be Continued!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.99,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'm finally on vacation!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:12.89,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my swimsuit?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:14.45,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,It may be a resort, \Nbut it's the middle of winter!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:15.77,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. It's almost Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:17.50,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to give me, Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:18.75,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Something round and golden.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.75,0:23:19.52,Default,V,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:20.85,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Tenth Skate:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:27.00,Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16}Tenth Skate \N{\fs20}Gotta Supercharge It! \NPre-Grand Prix Final Special!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:22.00,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta Supercharge It!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:24.08,Default,Y,0000,0000,0000,,Pre-Grand Prix Final Special!
